  "detailed_description": "<strong>[Game Introduction]</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/e1b51228e743b083de665a22fc734f92.avif?t=1695697620\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br>The ROOT series is a fantasy 3D RPG game project where you travel through five cities inhabited by humans, undead, dwarves, and forgotten beings, complete given quests, follow the stories within the quests, and grow your character.<br><br><strong>[Game Story]</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/a5a57c148aa5dc54439af15c9be8cf68.poster.avif?t=1695697620\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/a5a57c148aa5dc54439af15c9be8cf68.webm?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/a5a57c148aa5dc54439af15c9be8cf68.mp4?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As the responsible party for Project S, the project to prepare for the apocalypse, go back in time to save the war-ravaged world. Hone your skills, craft equipment, and deal with the forces trying to hinder the project. Survive in the desolate wastelands, lava zones, and swamps inhabited by monsters, and remember, to secure the future, you must unravel your past.<br><br><strong>[Features]</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Crossing the End of the World</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c746544726936cfd3f80764cfc5dd47e.poster.avif?t=1695697620\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c746544726936cfd3f80764cfc5dd47e.webm?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c746544726936cfd3f80764cfc5dd47e.mp4?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You are tasked with going back in time to prevent the war that caused the world's devastation. However, your contact with other cooperating cities, which provide materials for the mission, has been severed due to the war. You must venture into the arid wastelands and lava zones while clearing obstacles to secure the necessary materials. Choose a profession, constantly refine your skills and equipment, as all other lifeforms have gone berserk in anticipation of the impending apocalypse.<br><br></li><li><strong>Following Truth and the Past</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c9649124e20af1947aeacf22109ece07.poster.avif?t=1695697620\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c9649124e20af1947aeacf22109ece07.webm?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c9649124e20af1947aeacf22109ece07.mp4?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Why did your contact with the cooperating cities suddenly break? Could they be hiding something? Even though the only way to prevent the apocalypse may disappear, their attitude seems peculiar. And perhaps the behavior of the monsters is also peculiar. At the brink of this apocalypse, what are they hiding?<br><br></li><li><strong>Gathering and Crafting or Buying</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c6b188ca494dd67cff1f14786cecb6c5.poster.avif?t=1695697620\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c6b188ca494dd67cff1f14786cecb6c5.webm?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c6b188ca494dd67cff1f14786cecb6c5.mp4?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Embark on your adventure, where you must do almost everything yourself. Gather minerals and herbs from the surroundings, hunt monsters to collect resources. Utilize these resources to craft the weapons, armor, or potions you desire, or sell them to merchants to accumulate capital for equipment.<br><br></li><li><strong>Equipment Maintenance</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/4d3baf594dbe3a3ae9139edc01cadb8e.poster.avif?t=1695697620\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/4d3baf594dbe3a3ae9139edc01cadb8e.webm?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/4d3baf594dbe3a3ae9139edc01cadb8e.mp4?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Utilize special items such as gems and enchantment dust, obtained through gathering and hunting, to enhance the performance of your equipment. Use them to improve your health, defense, mana, and energy. Obtain higher-tier special items through hunting, gathering, and crafting.<br><br></li><li><strong>Achieve Challenges</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/a6565889197ff3275e3bdf053f8e5ee3.poster.avif?t=1695697620\" width=620 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/a6565889197ff3275e3bdf053f8e5ee3.webm?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/a6565889197ff3275e3bdf053f8e5ee3.mp4?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>See how much you've grown as a hero within the game. Reflect on the connections you've made. During your playthrough, you'll discover how great a hero you truly are.<br><br></li><li><strong>Open Development</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/1c4e2681ec75d926078a2920c7ff6925.poster.avif?t=1695697620\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/1c4e2681ec75d926078a2920c7ff6925.webm?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/1c4e2681ec75d926078a2920c7ff6925.mp4?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you encounter any inconveniences or areas for improvement within the game, please feel free to visit the community and provide feedback. The SJR Team values player feedback.<br>Community Link: </li></ul><br><strong>[About the Development Team]</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/b7d0c2a3e6bad47753119384becd5865.avif?t=1695697620\" width=250 height=250 /></span><br>Team Instagram Link: <br>SJR Team is a game development team that has developed various games and is currently working on game development projects.<br>SJR Team has been recognized in various national competitions and support programs, with notable works including THE FIFTH, Do11, and Shape Of Liberty.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>[Game Introduction]</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/e1b51228e743b083de665a22fc734f92.avif?t=1695697620\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br>The ROOT series is a fantasy 3D RPG game project where you travel through five cities inhabited by humans, undead, dwarves, and forgotten beings, complete given quests, follow the stories within the quests, and grow your character.<br><br><strong>[Game Story]</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/a5a57c148aa5dc54439af15c9be8cf68.poster.avif?t=1695697620\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/a5a57c148aa5dc54439af15c9be8cf68.webm?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/a5a57c148aa5dc54439af15c9be8cf68.mp4?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As the responsible party for Project S, the project to prepare for the apocalypse, go back in time to save the war-ravaged world. Hone your skills, craft equipment, and deal with the forces trying to hinder the project. Survive in the desolate wastelands, lava zones, and swamps inhabited by monsters, and remember, to secure the future, you must unravel your past.<br><br><strong>[Features]</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Crossing the End of the World</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c746544726936cfd3f80764cfc5dd47e.poster.avif?t=1695697620\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c746544726936cfd3f80764cfc5dd47e.webm?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c746544726936cfd3f80764cfc5dd47e.mp4?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You are tasked with going back in time to prevent the war that caused the world's devastation. However, your contact with other cooperating cities, which provide materials for the mission, has been severed due to the war. You must venture into the arid wastelands and lava zones while clearing obstacles to secure the necessary materials. Choose a profession, constantly refine your skills and equipment, as all other lifeforms have gone berserk in anticipation of the impending apocalypse.<br><br></li><li><strong>Following Truth and the Past</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c9649124e20af1947aeacf22109ece07.poster.avif?t=1695697620\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c9649124e20af1947aeacf22109ece07.webm?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c9649124e20af1947aeacf22109ece07.mp4?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Why did your contact with the cooperating cities suddenly break? Could they be hiding something? Even though the only way to prevent the apocalypse may disappear, their attitude seems peculiar. And perhaps the behavior of the monsters is also peculiar. At the brink of this apocalypse, what are they hiding?<br><br></li><li><strong>Gathering and Crafting or Buying</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c6b188ca494dd67cff1f14786cecb6c5.poster.avif?t=1695697620\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c6b188ca494dd67cff1f14786cecb6c5.webm?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/c6b188ca494dd67cff1f14786cecb6c5.mp4?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Embark on your adventure, where you must do almost everything yourself. Gather minerals and herbs from the surroundings, hunt monsters to collect resources. Utilize these resources to craft the weapons, armor, or potions you desire, or sell them to merchants to accumulate capital for equipment.<br><br></li><li><strong>Equipment Maintenance</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/4d3baf594dbe3a3ae9139edc01cadb8e.poster.avif?t=1695697620\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/4d3baf594dbe3a3ae9139edc01cadb8e.webm?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/4d3baf594dbe3a3ae9139edc01cadb8e.mp4?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Utilize special items such as gems and enchantment dust, obtained through gathering and hunting, to enhance the performance of your equipment. Use them to improve your health, defense, mana, and energy. Obtain higher-tier special items through hunting, gathering, and crafting.<br><br></li><li><strong>Achieve Challenges</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/a6565889197ff3275e3bdf053f8e5ee3.poster.avif?t=1695697620\" width=620 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/a6565889197ff3275e3bdf053f8e5ee3.webm?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/a6565889197ff3275e3bdf053f8e5ee3.mp4?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>See how much you've grown as a hero within the game. Reflect on the connections you've made. During your playthrough, you'll discover how great a hero you truly are.<br><br></li><li><strong>Open Development</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/1c4e2681ec75d926078a2920c7ff6925.poster.avif?t=1695697620\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/1c4e2681ec75d926078a2920c7ff6925.webm?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/1c4e2681ec75d926078a2920c7ff6925.mp4?t=1695697620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you encounter any inconveniences or areas for improvement within the game, please feel free to visit the community and provide feedback. The SJR Team values player feedback.<br>Community Link: </li></ul><br><strong>[About the Development Team]</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183360/extras/b7d0c2a3e6bad47753119384becd5865.avif?t=1695697620\" width=250 height=250 /></span><br>Team Instagram Link: <br>SJR Team is a game development team that has developed various games and is currently working on game development projects.<br>SJR Team has been recognized in various national competitions and support programs, with notable works including THE FIFTH, Do11, and Shape Of Liberty.",
